Predict allometric parameters from DBH

Source: R/allometry_pred.R
predict_allometry.Rd

Predict allometric parameters from DBH

predict_allometry(
  input_dbh_cm,
  parameter = c("Bark_cm", "Sap_cm", "Saparea_cm2"),
  species = NULL,
  ...
)

Arguments

input_dbh_cm

numeric, single value or vector of DBH measurements in cm

parameter

character, one or multiple of "Bark_cm", "Sap_cm", "Saparea_cm2"

species

character, one or multiple of the species given in allometry.data. Defaults to NULL, selecting all species.

...

additional arguments passed to predict()

Value

A data.frame containing predictions for each provided parameter and species
